<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實，<delay20 />我跟<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />
借了一樣東西，<delay20 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是一直都找不到歸還的時機<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />日子就這樣一天一天過去，<delay20 />
我也越來越不好意思<delay20 />
開口還<gender3 m="他" f="她" />東西了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我去幫你還</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />加油！</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不久之前，<delay20 />我和<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><delay8 />
一起在我家<delay20 />
喝茶聊天<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><delay20 />
卻把東西忘在我家，就這樣回去了。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想把東西送去給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />，<delay20 />
但是我也有事情要忙，<delay8 />
還沒辦法拿給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />。
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />實在很不好意思，<delay20 />
可以拜託你<delay8 />
替我把東西送去給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">交給我吧！</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">抱歉喔</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了對了，<delay20 />
你可以聽我說一下嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說我收到了一個包裹，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />仔細一看，<delay8 />才發現那包裹居然不是我的，<delay8 />
而是<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的呢。
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />幸好我在打開之前就發現了，<delay20 />
可是我想<gender3 m="他" f="她" />現在一定很困擾，<delay20 />
真希望能快點把包裹送去給<gender3 m="他" f="她" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我幫你送去吧</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一路順風</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦！？<delay20 />真的嗎！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要拜託你還的就是這個，<delay20 />
麻煩你了！</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />非常感謝你！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼，<delay20 />這個就麻煩你了。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦！？<delay20 />非常感謝你！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我就不客氣了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要拜託你送去的就是這個，<delay8 />麻煩你了。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好的，<delay20 />我會加油的。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不然我一直想著得把東西還回去，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />心裡總是有負擔呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想也是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />對不起。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對方現在一定很困擾，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還是<delay8 />我送過去吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我知道了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然包裹有點重，<delay20 />
我還是會努力送到的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以<delay20 />打擾你一下嗎！？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說，<delay20 />我準備了一份禮物
要送給平時對我照顧有加的<delay20 />
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我原本是想自己拿給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />的，<delay20 />
可是有點提不起勇氣，<delay20 />
所以一直都<delay8 />沒辦法拿給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />呢<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
我知道這樣會造成你的麻煩，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過你能不能幫我拿給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我幫你拿吧</message>
	<message label="101_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />加油！</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以請你<delay20 />聽我說嗎？<pageBreak />其實，<delay20 />前陣子我和
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />吵了一架。<pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得自己當時說得太過分了，<delay8 />
所以我好好反省之後，<delay20 />
就試著準備了和好的禮物<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是我不知道該怎麼拿給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />，<delay8 />
所以禮物<delay20 /><anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在還在我這裡。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不好意思，好像把你捲進來了，<delay20 />
不過可以拜託你<delay8 />
替我把禮物拿給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我幫你拿去吧</message>
	<message label="102_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你還是自己拿去吧？</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />非常感謝你！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
那麼，能麻煩你<delay20 />把這個禮物送過去嗎？</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太好了～<delay frames="40" />
非常謝謝你。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要拜託你的就是這個，<delay20 />麻煩你囉！</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽到你這麼說，我就稍微有點勇氣了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然非常難為情，<delay20 />但我會努力鼓起勇氣，<delay8 />
試著自己送過去的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說的也有道理呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我知道了，<delay20 />
我會拿出勇氣，<delay8 /><anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />親自送過去的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不好意思，要求你這麼多……<delay20 />
希望能在今天之內送到，麻煩你囉，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天時間也已經<delay8 />有點晚了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
你可以明天再送過去<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也沒關係喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那麼就麻煩你<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />代替我把跟<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />借的東西
還給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />囉，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />忘了帶走的東西……<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請你一定要記得<delay8 />還給<gender3 m="他" f="她" />喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的東西，<delay20 />
就放在我交給你的包裹裡，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />麻煩你直接轉交給本人囉，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我交給你的那個禮物，<delay20 />
請你要若無其事地<delay8 />
拿給<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我交給你的那個禮物<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
就請你轉交給
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />囉。<pageBreak /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唉～<delay20 />我好緊張喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>